<h2>
    WMS Server Demo</h2>
<div class="hero-unit">
    <p>
        This shows demonstrates implementing a tile server. There are various ways to implement a tile server - WMTS, XYZ, TMS
    </p>
    <p>
        <div id="attrs">
            &nbsp;
        </div>
    </p>
    <div id="map" class="smallmap">
    </div>
    <p>
    </p>
